msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt01_Desc"
msgid ""
"Rumor has it there's an item called the\n"
"Korok Mask that has the power to alert its\n"
"wearer when a Korok is hiding nearby.\n"
"\n"
"Apparently the <1.se_co>Woodland Stable<2.re_co> has a copy of\n"
"Super Rumor Mill EX, which details some rumors\n"
"about this rare mask."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt01_Finish"
msgid ""
"You found the <1.se_co>Korok Mask<2.re_co> in the spooky tree's\n"
"hollow within the Lost Woods!\n"
"\n"
"The Korok Mask will inform you when a Korok\n"
"is hiding nearby."
msgstr ""

