msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt01_Step01"
msgid ""
"You read Super Rumor Mill EX: Volume 1!\n"
"According to this special issue, there are\n"
"rumors of an item called the Korok Mask\n"
"that has been inhabited by a friendly spirit.\n"
"\n"
"The treasure chest containing the Korok Mask\n"
"is hidden <1.se_co>in the hollow of a terrifying tree in a\n"
"forest that causes those who enter to lose their\n"
"way<2.re_co>. Find that forest and locate the treasure\n"
"chest! It also seems there's a convenient way\n"
"to search for it..."
msgstr ""

